<div class="container account">
  <div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <% if current_ico_user.eth_wallet.nil? %>
        <p><strong>Fill in your ETH/ETZ wallet to get investment info</strong></p>
            <%= form_tag controller: 'account', action: 'add_eth', method: 'POST', class: 'inline-form' do %>
                <%= text_field_tag :eth_wallet, '', class: "form-control", placeholder: 'ETH/ETZ wallet'  %>
                <%= submit_tag t(:submit), class: "button red" %>
            <% end %>
      <% end %>
        <strong>The smart contract address:</strong>
        <p><%= 'Will be available on ICO' if current_ico_user.eth_wallet.present? %></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Min pledge is 0.1 ETH;</li>
          <li>Set GAS 300 000 (unused gas will be returned to you);</li>
          <li>We recommend to use myetherwallet.com</li>
        </ul>
        <strong>The ETZ wallet for investing:</strong>
        <p><%= 'Will be available on ICO' if current_ico_user.eth_wallet.present? %></p>
        <div class="pb-2">Transfer ETZ tutorials for all possible wallets <a href="http://etherzero.org/tutorials/" class="text-secondary">http://etherzero.org/tutorials/</a></div>
        <div class="pb-2"><strong>Attention:</strong> minimal amount 10 ETZ. The fee is less than the amount claimed for the accrual of RDT will not be processed.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <% if current_ico_user.eth_wallet.present? %>
        <div class="row">
              <div class="col my-2">
                <div class="alert alert-primary h-100"><div class="text-center h3"><span id="eth_balance"><%= "%g"%@etz_investments.sum(:rdt) %></span> RDT</div><div class="h5 text-center">Balance</div></div>
              </div>
          <div class="col my-2">
            <div class="alert alert-primary h-100"><div class="text-center h3"><%= @referrals %></div><div class="h5 text-center">Referrals</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="col my-2">
            <div class="alert alert-primary h-100"><div class="text-center h3"><%= @referrals*10 %> RDT</div><div class="h5 text-center">Referral Bonus</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
            <div>
              Your referral link to participate in the Bounty program:
              <strong><%= ref_link %></strong><br>
              Your ETH wallet: <span id="eth_wallet" class="text-truncate d-inline-block w-100"><%= current_ico_user.eth_wallet %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="h4">Purchase History(ETH)</div>
            <table class="table table-light table-striped">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Time</th>
                  <th>ETH</th>
                  <th>RDT</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="purchase_history_data"></tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="h4">Purchase History(ETZ)</div>
            <table class="table table-light table-striped">
              <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Time</th>
                <th>ETZ</th>
                <th>RDT</th>
              </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="purchase_history_data">
                <% @etz_investments.each do |i| %>
                  <tr>
                    <td>
                      <%= i.time.to_s %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <%= "%g"%i.etz %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <%= "%g"%i.rdt %>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                <% end %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="h4">Bounty Program</p>
    <p>Any user who has an own website, blog or social network account can take our Bounty Rate Date program. User is rewarded with 10RTD for each potential investor, engaged by him before starting ICO or during it. User can receive additional rewarding of 100RTD if investor engaged by him deposits any funds into ICO program. Rewarding arrives in a wallet balance, pointed in a personal account.</p>
    <p><strong>ATTENTION!</strong> Do not use online exchanges addresses or another’s ones. Use only your own addresses which you can fully control. Otherwise your RDT would be lost.</p>
  </div>
</div>